settings.description: You have to do the least logical thing to escape from jail, if you did the least logical thing you win and if not you will stay lost in an endless loop.
Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.
If you are casual player, this is so hard, if you are not a casual player, it is easy.
